subject: Baseball
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: In the Mets’ victory over the Astros, R. A. Dickey continued to demonstrate that he could perform at the highest level of his sport. Now he wants to show he can do it in another sport as a ball boy at the United States Open.
